title: Unboxing Dell U2917W Monitor & First Impressions
description:
I managed to borrow a Dell U2917W monitor from Dell SIngapore for a review. The 21:9 aspect ratio is cool! My full review from an artist/graphic designer perspective will be out in a few weeks time.

Full specs on Dell's website:
